  <brief_title>Rétrospective Evaluation of the Performance and the Safety of the Endoscopic Mucosectomy With Anchorage</brief_title>
  <official_title>Rétrospective Evaluation of the Performance and the Safety of the Endoscopic Mucosectomy With Anchorage of the Tip of the Loop</official_title>
